# Graffiti: The Water Stealers

**Location / Context:** Lower-level Ceres docking area, often found near water reclamation units.
**Visual Description:** Accompanied by a hastily sprayed OPA split-circle symbol.

**English Text:**
> __they#CL2 drink#CL2 water#CL6 1PL#POSS breathe#1PL dust#CL9 they.#POSS#CL2 belt#CL9 provide#CL9 BENREFL.__
"They drink our water, we breathe their dust. The Belt provides for itself."
